text: Debrzyno is a settlement in the administrative district of Gmina Kościerzyna, within Kościerzyna County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately south of Kościerzyna and south-west of the regional capital Gdańsk. For details of the history of the region, see History of Pomerania. ==References== Debrzyno
